Detailed Description

The RDF representation for type="http://www.cellml.org/RDFXML/string"

Member Data Documentation

attribute wstring cellml_api::RDFXMLStringRepresentation::serialisedData

A complete RDF/XML document (including a single top-level RDF:rdf element) as a serialised string. Fetching the attribute again will update to the latest data. Assigning this attribute to a new string will cause the string to be parsed as RDF/XML, and all RDF in the model will be replaced with the resulting RDF/XML tree.
